        <item>
            <title>v1.0.3</title>
            <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jun 2026 01:13:04 +0000</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Search list now refreshes after updating the cache. Choosing "Check for Cache Update" (Cmd-R) now shows newly available shows right away — no need to quit and relaunch.</li>
<li>Toolbar tooltips work in icon-only mode. Hovering over a toolbar button now explains what it does, even when the button is disabled.</li>
<li>PVR and Download History are now in the Window menu. Open them directly with Cmd-P and Cmd-Y.</li>
<li>Windows reopen where you left them. Window positions are now properly restored when you relaunch the app.</li>
</ul>]]></description>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.6.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <enclosure
                url="https://github.com/Ascoware/get-iplayer-automator-2/releases/download/v1.0.3/Get.iPlayer.Automator.2.v1.0.3.b202606291808.zip"
