        </item>
        <item>
            <title>v1.0.2</title>
            <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jun 2026 00:57:20 +0000</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>
<p>Automatic software updates now work. Get iPlayer Automator 2 checks for new<br>
versions in the background, and a new "Check for Updates…" item in the<br>
application menu lets you check on demand.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Important: because of a bug in the updater, versions 1.0.0 and 1.0.1 could<br>
not update themselves. If you're on one of those builds, please install this<br>
version manually this one time — automatic updates will work from here on.</p>
</li>
</ul>]]></description>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.6.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <enclosure
                url="https://github.com/Ascoware/get-iplayer-automator-2/releases/download/v1.0.2/Get.iPlayer.Automator.2.v1.0.2.b202606281753.zip"
                sparkle:version="202606281753"
